{\pntext\f0 1.\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlbody\pnf0\pnindent0\pnstart1\pndec{\pntxta.}}
\fi-360\li720 Added BackupUtil.exe to Program Files\\EQLogParser that can be used from the command line. It works similar to the Create Backup options. When running the application you pass it a --path for the directory you'd like the zip file to be created in and nothing else.\par
{\pntext\f0 2.\tab}Updated the Restore process to handle error cases and roll back changes if needed.\par
{\pntext\f0 3.\tab}Updated Splash screen to have options for opening the error log and closing the app in the case where a critical error happens and the screen doesn't go away.\par
