{\pntext\f0 2.\tab}Added some basic fast check similar support to further help with trigger performance.\par
{\pntext\f0 3.\tab}Cached default overlay queries to avoid errors where sometimes those overlays would not be found as it causes too many DB queries.\par
{\pntext\f0 4.\tab}Additional optimizations for timer overlays.\par
{\pntext\f0 5.\tab}Added a Clear button to Trigger Tester to avoid having to select all/delete when you pasted a large number of lines. There is a bug with the text viewer where it may sometimes crash when doing that. The button should help avoid those cases.\par
{\pntext\f0 6.\tab}Added All Players option to Spell Counts right-click. It includes all verified players across all summaries.\par
{\pntext\f0 7.\tab}Added hours to the timer bar if needed.\par
